Assets.Name: CustomMaps
Assets.Description:
Hello everyone

UPDATE:  Fixes
-collisions have been reworked to use UCX so grinds should work better
-tweaked heights of some objects
-I modeled the collision on rails so that they have gaps under the rail.  In theory you should be able to hippie flip
-Applied physical materials
-Removed audio so ears can stop bleeding
-Remodeled rail objects

Feel free to let me know of any more bugs you find and I’ll try to get them with another update if it needs it.  Other than that, I hope you enjoy it!
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1IFWsQoqZdzwDGxfHQrSrmWZcl57rbPFW/view?usp=sharingMy first attempt at making a custom map for session.  Go easy on her.  Hopefully it’s fun to skate.  Started out as a test for bringing things from blender into ue4 and just kinda snowballed from there.  Loosely based on a skatepark near Zakim Bridge.  
Huge thanks goes out to <@!156600986251689984> for all the help with getting marketplace assets to work and shadows to show up.  I was getting frustrated and almost deleted it.  But, I didn’t.  So here you go.  Hopefully someone enjoys it.  https://drive.google.com/file/d/12MkOSaR05P8B1rkcy4aCimbyIwpB75EL/view
